  <paragraphs xml:id="homework">
    <title>Homework</title>
    <p>
    Homework will be assigned daily and due two class periods later. Each problem will be graded on a scale from 0 to 3. A grade of 0 indicates there is nothing correct about your solution. A grade of 3 indicates your solution is correct with no mistakes. A grade of 2 is mostly correct, with minor mistakes. A grade of 1 has a correct idea, but needs some serious work.
    </p>

  </paragraphs>

  <paragraphs xml:id="midterm-exams">
    <title>Midterm Exams</title>
    <p>
      There will be three midterm exams given in class on 2/6, 3/6, and 4/10. The class day before exams will be reserved for review. 
    </p>
  </paragraphs>
